name: Immoral X-Men (2023) @1
summary:
PART 4: THE BOND AGE

ADORED AND RESPECTED! They said the mutants were humanity's future. It's 10 years later and they were proven to be right. The X-Men exist in a world that adores and respects them…so why are they sworn to crush it?! But while they do, Emma can take a few minutes out to crush Mister Sinister.

SINS OF SINISTER TIE-IN

name: Immoral X-Men (2023) @2
summary:
PART 6: FOUR-LETTER WORDS

PUTTING THE “DIE” IN DIAMOND AGE! Hail the Pax Krakoa! Or perish! But to this hell age is born a hero. Say hello (again) to Rasputin IV...but what can one good chimera do in a universe of sin? The first century of Sinister’s plan has come to an end…and whether it’s better or worse may depend on the symbol on your forehead.

SINS OF SINISTER TIE-IN
